One thing to realize is that every time we turn around, scientists are saying, oh actually we were wrong, climate change is way worse than we thought.

2
00:00:07,860 --> 00:00:12,965
So, we need to look at everything through a lens of environmental justice.

3
00:00:14,527 --> 00:00:17,851
The Green Justice Coalition has the right idea which is to put together

4
00:00:19,613 --> 00:00:28,600
Marginalized communities of color that are most impacted by climate change with labor and environmental groups, and that is how we develop a Green New Deal.

5
00:00:29,621 --> 00:00:34,726
We have to commit to sourcing our electricity from 100% renewables by 2035 at the latest.

6
00:00:37,348 --> 00:00:38,768
We have to divest from fossil fuels.

7
00:00:39,609 --> 00:00:43,770
We have to convert government transportation to electric.

8
