We have to make sure that all new housing is passive housing, is zero emissions housing.

9
00:00:50,391 --> 00:00:59,053
But more than that, we are eventually going to have to have a plan for how are we going to switch our private transportation to electric?

10
00:00:59,433 --> 00:01:06,075
How are we going to retrofit all of our housing and commercial buildings so that they are not

11
