also emitting carbon emissions.

12
00:01:10,756 --> 00:01:13,357
And so it's a very complex problem.

13
00:01:13,377 --> 00:01:25,080
And again, the way we go about it is through a coalition of groups that really centralizes the voices of the people most impacted by climate change.

14
00:01:26,360 --> 00:01:33,304
